{"tid":852580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(新八國聯軍) 歐盟促港府澄清拒向馬凱續發工作簽證原因","createTime":"2018-10-08T03:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T12:12:28.000Z","uid":7369,"like":109,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a22879952cd7e08f345f5f456f6762c58eb233","tid":852580,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:04:33.000Z","msg":"任職《金融時報》的外國記者會副主席馬凱被特區政府拒續發工作簽證，繼英國要求港府立即解釋、美國炮轟港府做法不符《基本法》後，今日連歐盟也發聲，質疑有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲聯盟駐港澳辦事處發言人回覆查詢時指，歐盟正密切留意事件，並期望香港政府澄清拒絕向一名記者發出簽證的原因，歐盟又為香港表達和新聞自由本受《基本法》和《公民權利及政治權利國際公約》所保障，如今卻引起一個正式疑問。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟駐港澳辦事處回覆查詢全文：<br />\nThe EU is following this issue closely and expects the HK government to clarify the reasons of the refusal to grant visa to a journalist. This incident raises legitimate questions about the freedom of press and expression in HK, which are guaranteed by HK&rsquo;s Basic Law and ICCPR.&quot; <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181008/58769179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58769179&d=iI5Tuu4jwIiV0%2BmkkSMa5dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=0be0b50f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58769179&h=14af2925\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181008/58769179</a>"},{"pid":"75a85512520dbb27b61c8ca1c44038e1a8f7eeb0","tid":852580,"uid":186814,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"唔好認衰仔呀 要奶盡d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14007d8521f66ee0e18a5b0a209ce1edc15974ea","tid":852580,"uid":17866,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:06:49.000Z","msg":"不容白人說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即日處決港內所有白人，頭掛金紫荊示眾"},{"pid":"62f6353b8c5e75bce7079593102fa3736f6f3b13